{"tid":1432402,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警鄧炳強去左邊？","createTime":"2019-08-08T08:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T13:26:53.000Z","uid":218615,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d7d5ce1e249a49abdb852bb942965109a586ad38","tid":1432402,"uid":218615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:35:12.000Z","msg":"鄧炳強，PDSM（英語：TANG Ping-keung, Chris，1965年7月4日－），曾於中國浦東幹部學院、中國人民公安大學受訓，現任香港警務處副處長（行動）。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強於中國浦東幹部學院、中國人民公安大學受訓，回港後開始擔任各區指揮官角色，2015年晉升至助理處長，任港島總區指揮官，現主管人事部。多名前線警官透露，鄧炳強處事圓滑，2013年離任元朗警區指揮官時，獲鄉紳在小桃園酒家設江湖飯宴歡送，當中包括前屏山鄉鄉委會主席綽號「高佬和」曾樹和。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強與一眾新界鄉紳和黑幫有千絲萬縷關係，為人詬病，在他擔任元朗警區指揮官期間，被質疑多次包庇和縱容新界鄉黑勢力，任內因元朗警區幾宗警察醜聞，包括將「白粉（海洛因）當鹽」處理，需要勞煩警察公共關係科為鄧炳強解畫，甚至親自致電游說各大媒體的採訪主任，要傳媒筆下留情，為醜聞降溫。2019年7月21日，黑幫成員在元朗襲擊大量市民，身為警務處副處長（行動）的鄧炳強，被指默許鄉黑勢力襲擊大量平民，元朗區議員黃偉賢擔心警黑之間的關係逐漸成為一種默契，元朗治安持續惡化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一開頭唔係好威威話要承擔所有責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家龜縮左去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd5879cedd70ab6f8c410365fe458e135ad9278","tid":1432402,"uid":273760,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:36:16.000Z","msg":"做左特首啦"},{"pid":"32464c4694c552c2eef5f3997e83f62c2c1e7da8","tid":1432402,"uid":4574,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:41:53.000Z","msg":"支持鄧小強 <br />\n軍政府大統領<br />\n幾時反攻大陸？"},{"pid":"9dc51a62ad4ed6939a4d91cfb33dbaa6d3591f8e","tid":1432402,"uid":218615,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:42:36.000Z","msg":"鄧sir好波呀<br />\n叫班鄉親入元朗搞事<br />\n威風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdae7086167af57b45a21523f3da7b6918ccd51","tid":1432402,"uid":73509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:42:54.000Z","msg":"而家香港係由軍政府統領，佢地阿頭鄧炳強好忙啦"},{"pid":"30b3bfa83fdd3c1f8b761f13a836027b20818810","tid":1432402,"uid":145254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:43:21.000Z","msg":"狗大哥呢？"},{"pid":"d52bc2ab45f0ecafab952be97bd353bd167486c1","tid":1432402,"uid":261937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:19:09.000Z","msg":"係小桃園招呼緊褔建佬"},{"pid":"54b62d17475c0ecce3c2ca1eb34b42fcb3a8b4fb","tid":1432402,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:26:05.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"b1000d01f83703a619f6b35a9cbca8cdd55a25b4","tid":1432402,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:29:53.000Z","msg":"聽聞去左幫散仔福利會林主席含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8cc473571e10310669c5fc7cd5dc82ca2d4725","tid":1432402,"uid":218615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c6fed1fede05fab3d9142b0144d43bcef2cac7","tid":1432402,"uid":292717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:00:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190808/mobile/bkn-20190808171625606-0808_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190808%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190808171625606-0808_00822_001.html&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO74hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=89baf3cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190808/mobile/bkn-20190808171625606-0808_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"94d74b2e4d17836fbb25996a2cf43eff3dfd35fa","tid":1432402,"uid":218615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14c6fed1fede05fab3d9142b0144d43bcef2cac7","tid":1432402,"uid":292717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:00:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190808/mobile/bkn-20190808171625606-0808_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190808%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190